The '''Kingsizegala''' is an annual music award hosted by the [[Sweden|Swedish]] music magazine ''Kingsize Magazine''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gp.se/parham-kan-bli-storvinnare-p%C3%A5-kingsizegalan-1.273092?|title=Parham kan bli storvinnare på Kingsizegalan|publisher=|accessdate=7 September 2016}}</ref> It mainly covers the hip hop music scene.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv4.se/kingsizegalan|title=Kingsizegalan – tv4.se|publisher=tv4.se|accessdate=7 September 2016}}</ref> Since 2014, the awards ceremony is broadcast live on [[TV4 (Sweden)|TV4 Play]].<ref>
*{{cite web|url=http://www.tv4.se/kingsizegalan/artiklar/h%C3%A4r-%C3%A4r-artisterna-som-upptr%C3%A4der-live-p%C3%A5-kingsizegalan-2014-52e23ccdc4594809c5000008|title=Här är artisterna som uppträder live på Kingsizegalan 2014 – Kingsizegalan – tv4.se|publisher=|accessdate=7 September 2016}}
*{{cite web|url=http://www.kingsizemagazine.se/noje/se-hela-kingsizegalan-2015-via-tv4-play/|title=Se hela Kingsizegalan 2015 via TV4 Play!|publisher=kingsizemagazine|accessdate=7 September 2016}}</ref>  In 2015 the gala was hosted at the [[Annexet]] in [[Stockholm]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kingsizemagazine.se/noje/vinnarna-pa-kingsizegalan-2015-se-listan-har/|title=Vinnarna på KINGSIZEGALAN 2015 – se listan här!|publisher=|accessdate=7 September 2016}}</ref>

